*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&      Form  FRM_MSG
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*       text
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
*      -->P_E_RETURN[]  text
*      -->P_LT_RETURN_BAPI[]  text
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM FRM_MSG  TABLES   P1 STRUCTURE BAPIRET2
                       P2 STRUCTURE BAPIRET2 .
  MOVE-CORRESPONDING P2[] TO P1[] .
ENDFORM.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&      Form  FRM_MSG4
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*       text
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
*      -->P_E_RETURN[]  text
*      -->P_E_MSG2[]  text
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM FRM_MSG4  TABLES   P1 STRUCTURE BAPIRET2
                        P2 STRUCTURE BAPI_METH_MESSAGE.
  LOOP AT P2 .
    P1-TYPE = P2-MESSAGE_TYPE.
    P1-ID = P2-MESSAGE_ID.
    P1-NUMBER = P2-MESSAGE_NUMBER.
    P1-MESSAGE = P2-MESSAGE_TEXT.
    APPEND P1 .
    CLEAR P1 .
  ENDLOOP.
ENDFORM.
